C     ICPC 2020 ASIA TAIPEI: PROBLEM G (GRAPH CARDS)
C     SUBJECTIVE REALIZATION: FULL CROW PUPPETRY LIFECYCLE
C     VALIDATING 1MB ARENA (LEVEL 11 REDUCTION / 2048 LEAVES)
      PROGRAM Crow_Subjective_Realization
      ARENA CROW_ARENA SIZE 1048576
      
C     1. INITIALIZE SKELETON (16 JOINTS FOR HIGH-FIDELITY RESONANCE)
      WAVELET W_CROW FROM CROW_ARENA
      ATTACH_DATA W_CROW "NODES:16 EDGES:16 (1,2) (2,3) (3,4) (4,1) (1,5) (2,6) (3,7) (4,8) (5,9) (6,10) (7,11) (8,12) (9,13) (10,14) (11,15) (12,16)"
      
C     2. EXERCISE TASTE: CROW QUOTH (BEAK RESONANCE)
      EXERCISE_TASTE 0x414A
      SVDAG BEAK_DAG CAP 512
      ADD_OP BEAK_DAG TYPE KINEMATIC_ARTICULATE KERNEL 0 ENERGY 1.0 FREQ 0.414
      REDUCE W_CROW LEVEL 2 EPOCH 2 RESONANCE 414 DAG BEAK_DAG
      
C     3. EXERCISE TASTE: CROW SYMPATHY (SICKNESS INVERSION)
      EXERCISE_TASTE 0x414C
      SVDAG SICK_DAG CAP 512
      ADD_OP SICK_DAG TYPE SYMPATHY_MELT KERNEL 1 ENERGY 5.0 FREQ 50.0
      REDUCE W_CROW LEVEL 6 EPOCH 4 RESONANCE 414 DAG SICK_DAG
      
C     4. EXERCISE TASTE: CROW FLIGHT (KINETIC DIAMETER)
      EXERCISE_TASTE 0x120F
      SVDAG WING_DAG CAP 512
      ADD_OP WING_DAG TYPE RESONANCE KERNEL 2 ENERGY 15.0 FREQ 1.20
      REDUCE W_CROW LEVEL 8 EPOCH 6 RESONANCE 414 DAG WING_DAG
      
C     5. TERMINAL REALIZATION (FULL SKELETON ISOMORPHISM)
      REDUCE W_CROW LEVEL 11 EPOCH 8 RESONANCE 414
      AUDIT_SPIDER_TASTE W_CROW
      
C     6. LOG TELEMETRY FOR FULL VIDEO GENERATION
      LOG_TELEMETRY "Full Crow Subjective Realization stabilized in 1MB Manifold."
      END PROGRAM
